name: CryptoPrices
0:
”Alexa, open crypto prices and tell me the top ten”
”Alexa, open crypto prices and tell me the bitcoin price”
”Alexa, ask crypto prices for dogecoin price”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: crypto prices
des:
Crypto Prices allows you to get latest information (in real time) of cryptocurrency prices.

You can ask for the top ten cryptocurrencies by volume and also the price of most important coins.

Information provided by CryptoCompare.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
